data.description: Stunning 3 Bed, 2 Bath Home in Northwood. Welcome to this fully updated gem nestled in the exclusive community of Northwood. This elegant and spacious home boasts 4 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and a large fenced backyard, making it perfect for entertaining and enjoying a pool oasis.As you step inside, you're greeted by generous living areas that flow seamlessly into an inviting kitchen, ideal for culinary adventures and gatherings. The bedrooms are generously sized, offering ample closet space for storage needs.Outside, the beautiful backyard beckons with its potential for relaxation and outdoor fun. This property is conveniently located just minutes away from major highways such as the Turnpike and I-95, as well as popular destinations like Wellington, Boynton Beach, Downtown West Palm Beach and gorgeous area beaches. Additionally, access to three international airports adds to the convenience of this prime location.Don't miss the opportunity to make this exquisite home yours. Schedule a showing today and experience the epitome of Florida living!
